<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''細菌性陰道炎'''（{{lang|en|Bacterial vaginosis}}，簡稱'''BV'''），又稱'''細菌性陰道病'''、'''非特異性陰道炎'''（Nonspecific vaginitis）是種發生在[[陰道|陰道]]內的[[疾病|疾病]]，其原因是[[細菌|細菌]]大量滋生而造成的<ref name=Don2014/><ref name="ClarkTal2014">{{cite journal|last1=Clark|first1=Natalie|last2=Tal|first2=Reshef|last3=Sharma|first3=Harsha|last4=Segars|first4=James|title=Microbiota and Pelvic Inflammatory Disease|journal=Seminars in Reproductive Medicine|volume=32|issue=01|year=2014|pages=043–049|issn=1526-8004|doi=10.1055/s-0033-1361822|pmid=24390920|pmc=4148456}}</ref>。常見的症狀包括有[[陰道分泌物|陰道分泌物]]增加，而且分泌物有魚腥味<!-- <ref name=NIH2013S/> -->，且色澤多為白或灰色<!-- <ref name=NIH2013S/> -->。有時排尿時也會伴隨產生[[灼熱感|灼熱感]]<ref name=NIH2013S/>。搔癢則較不常見<ref name=Don2014/><ref name=NIH2013S/>，某些時候甚至可能完全沒有任何病徵出現<ref name=NIH2013S>{{cite web|title=What are the symptoms of bacterial vaginosis?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|accessdate=3 March 2015|date=2013-05-21|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402125344/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在感染細菌性陰道炎的情況下，另外感染其他[[性傳染病|性傳染病]]的機率大約提昇了一倍之多，而這當中包含了愛滋病（AIDS）<ref name=Ken2013>{{cite journal|last1=Kenyon|first1=C|last2=Colebunders|first2=R|last3=Crucitti|first3=T|title=The global epidemiology of bacterial vaginosis: a systematic review.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-obstetrics-and-gynecology_2013-12_209_6/page/505|journal=American Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecology|date=December 2013|volume=209|issue=6|pages=505–23|pmid=23659989|doi=10.1016/j.ajog.2013.05.006}}</ref><ref name=Bradshaw2015>{{cite journal|last1=Bradshaw|first1=CS|last2=Brotman|first2=RM|title=Making inroads into improving treatment of bacterial vaginosis - striving for long-term cure|journal=BMC Infectious Diseases|date=July 2015|volume=15|issue=|pages=292|pmid=26219949|pmc=4518586|doi=10.1186/s12879-015-1027-4}}</ref>。此疾病也連帶提高了產婦[[早產|早產]]的機率<ref name=Queenan2012>{{cite book|last1=Queena|first1=John T. .|last2=Spong|first2=Catherine Y|last3=Lockwood|first3=Charles J., editors|title=Queenan's management of high-risk pregnancy : an evidence-based approach|page=262|date=2012|publisher=Wiley-Blackwell|location=Chichester, West Sussex|isbn=9780470655764|edition=6th}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=What are the treatments for bacterial vaginosis (BV)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|publisher=National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=4 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402095211/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
細菌性陰道炎和存在於陰道內的原生細菌失衡有關<ref name=Bennett2015>{{cite book | last = Bennett | first = John | title = Mandell, Douglas, and Bennett's principles and practice of infectious diseases | publisher = Elsevier/Saunders | location = Philadelphia, PA | year = 2015 | isbn = 9781455748013}}</ref><ref name=NIH2013O/>。原先在陰道內常見的細菌發生了改變，且現有細菌數量以數百甚至數千倍的增加<ref name=Don2014/>。除了[[乳酸桿菌|乳酸桿菌]]外，多了非常多其他的細菌<ref name=Nardis2013>{{cite journal|last1=Nardis|first1=C.|last2=Mastromarino|first2=P.|last3=Mosca|first3=L.|title=Vaginal microbiota and viral sexually transmitted diseases|journal=Annali di Igiene |date=September–October 2013 |volume=25|issue=5|pages=443–56|doi=10.7416/ai.2013.1946|pmid=24048183}}</ref>。危險因子包括{{tsl|en|douching||沖洗陰道}}、新交或多重新伴侶、[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]還有使用[[子宮環|子宮環]]等<ref name=NIH2013O/>。但不管怎麼說，細菌性陰道炎並不屬於性傳染病的一種<ref name="cdc.gov">{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/std/bv/stdfact-bacterial-vaginosis.htm |title=Bacterial Vaginosis – CDC Fact Sheet |author= |date=March 11, 2014 |publisher=[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]] |accessdate=2 Mar 2015 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233757/https://www.cdc.gov/std/bv/stdfact-bacterial-vaginosis.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。診斷會建立在已有病症的情況下，接著檢測陰道分泌物再了解陰道內的[[pH值|pH值]]是否較正常為高，以及細菌數有無異常<ref name=Don2014/>。細菌性陰道炎常會和[[念珠菌性外阴阴道炎|念珠菌性外阴阴道炎]]或是[[滴虫性阴道炎|滴虫性阴道炎]]混淆<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Mashburn|first1=J|title=Etiology, diagnosis, and management of vaginitis.|journal=Journal of midwifery & women's health|date=2006|volume=51|issue=6|pages=423–30|pmid=17081932|doi=10.1016/j.jmwh.2006.07.005}}</ref>。

<!-- Prevention and treatment -->
治療細菌性陰道炎多使用抗生素，例如[[克林黴素|克林黴素]]或[[甲硝唑|甲硝唑]]<!-- <ref name=Don2014/> -->。這些藥物都可以在[[妊娠|孕期]]的第二或第三月期裡使用<!-- <ref name=Don2014/> -->但是，在治療過後又常有復發的情形<!-- <ref name=Don2014> -->。[[益生菌|益生菌]]據信可幫助預防降低復發的可能性<ref name=Don2014>{{cite journal|last1=Donders|first1=GG|last2=Zodzika|first2=J|last3=Rezeberga|first3=D|title=Treatment of bacterial vaginosis: what we have and what we miss.|journal=Expert opinion on pharmacotherapy|date=April 2014|volume=15|issue=5|pages=645–57|pmid=24579850|doi=10.1517/14656566.2014.881800}}</ref>。目前還不清楚在懷孕時使用益生菌或抗生素對孕婦是否有任何影響<ref name=Don2014/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Othman|first1=M|last2=Neilson|first2=JP|last3=Alfirevic|first3=Z|title=Probiotics for preventing preterm labour.|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|date=24 January 2007|issue=1|pages=CD005941|pmid=17253567|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005941.pub2}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology and history -->
細菌性陰道炎是育齡婦女常見的疾病<ref name=NIH2013O>{{cite web|title=Bacterial Vaginosis (BV): Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|publisher=National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=3 March 2015|date=2013-05-21|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402143838/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/bacterialvag/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在特定時間中，女性感染的比率大約介於5-70%<ref name=Ken2013/>。在非洲，女性患有此疾病的比例最高，但在亞洲與歐洲則都是相對較低的<ref name=Ken2013/>。美國的統計數據顯示，在14至49歲的女性中，罹患細菌性陰道炎的百分比約是30%<ref name=CDC2010Stats>{{cite web|title=Bacterial Vaginosis (BV) Statistics Prevalence|url=http://www.cdc.gov/std/bv/stats.htm|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=3 March 2015|date=September 14, 2010|archive-date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511071224/http://www.cdc.gov/std/bv/stats.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在每個國家裡，不同[[種族|種族]]的感染比率大不相同<ref name=Ken2013/>。歷史上，對於細菌性陰道炎的描述雖早已完備，但第一起有記錄在案的病例是1894年<ref name=History1997>{{cite book|last1=Borchardt|first1=Kenneth A.|title=Sexually transmitted diseases : epidemiology, pathology, diagnosis, and treatment|date=1997|publisher=CRC Press|location=Boca Raton [u.a.]|isbn=9780849394768|pages=4|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=k_9sjs-n0nIC&pg=PA4|access-date=2016-05-03|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225071600/https://books.google.ca/books?id=k_9sjs-n0nIC&pg=PA4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

